Class GoogleMapsLocator

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Locator, Locator_withExists

    public class GoogleMapsLocator
extends BaseLocator
    This locator is the entry point for the Google Maps library, providing access to all Google Maps services through the GoogleMapsManager .
